{"tid":1168164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★港爆？勁蝕八成都要沽！北角劏場地庫舖位32萬易手蝕讓","createTime":"2019-05-23T13:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T13:31:17.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f0adb9a0b7c71d1dfe43fbcfc0890fafdc745734","tid":1168164,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:21:14.000Z","msg":"商場劏舖大幅蝕讓。資料顯示，北角城市金庫地庫一個單號舖位，以32萬元登記易手，較2013年9月份購入價163.3萬元，大幅貶值約80.4%。<br />\n<br />\n屯門青山坊2號華樂大廈劏場壹號總站亦錄類似成交。該商場1樓雙號舖位以78萬元登記沽出，物業於2014年9月份購入，當時成交價約315.4萬元，即帳面蝕讓約75.2%。<br />\n<br />\n此外，旺角亞皆老街107號皆旺商業大廈2樓一個雙號舖，本月初以120萬元登記售出，較2012年7月購入價150萬元，低約20%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190523/bkn-20190523183455596-0523_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190523%2Fbkn-20190523183455596-0523_00842_001.html&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhEBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=c798a39a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190523/bkn-20190523183455596-0523_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"24ac6dbb9708f94bc9fbbd8f2b420f035f0dd4a1","tid":1168164,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc987b2a4090b2d1ad4f1eee1b70183b3eb8b87","tid":1168164,"uid":35408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"俾人當水魚<br />\n正常價沽出<br />\n咁都叫爆?"},{"pid":"a36cde60ba71b30f89f5591f8256956b43be9f27","tid":1168164,"uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:30:05.000Z","msg":"撲水返大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5213a95589081bbfe01a754c852d7ace90b5616b","tid":1168164,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a36cde60ba71b30f89f5591f8256956b43be9f27","tid":1168164,"uid":19609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T